        their ideal audience. Even with high-quality content, they often face
        challenges like low traffic, poor search engine rankings, and high
        bounce rates.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="h-full w-full pt-12 p-4">
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-4 md:gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white p-6 text-center shadow-xl">
